snippet.textDisplay:
Seems pointless to move to AM4 so late in its life, I play at 4K 60FPS on my FX3850 8 core 1080ti from doom no adaptive rez needed to Tomb Raider 1-3, Killing Floor 2, Dying Light. It all runs great. I can just upgrade my video card and get a far higher boost in FPS then upgrading into a dead end socket by 2022-23.

Save your money if you have a 6+ core cpu, go 12-16 core cheaper than it is now. Hell wont be surprised if 20-24 core cpu's will be out driving 16 core lower in price.
